# CLAUDE.md Template
> Layer 5 · Templates · Place this file at the **root of every repo** that implements UI

**Why:** Claude Code loads `CLAUDE.md` automatically every session — developers never need to paste the DS Context Block again (eliminating the human error that causes most DS violations).

**How to use:**
1. Copy the content below (from `<!-- START -->`) into a new `CLAUDE.md` at the repo root
2. Fill in the `[bracketed]` parts of the Project Context for that repo
3. Whenever the DS version bumps → the Maintainer syncs the "Design System Context" section in every repo (step 6 of the governance flow)

