# Project: [project name]

## Design System Context
- DS Name: [your team's DS name]
- DS Version: 1.2.0
- Manual: [link to the ai-design-manual repo]

### Color Tokens (token names only — never raw hex)
color.primary.50=#EFF6FF | 100=#DBEAFE | 500=#3B82F6 (default) | 600=#2563EB (hover) | 900=#1E3A8A
color.error.500=#EF4444 | color.warning.500=#F59E0B | color.success.500=#22C55E
color.neutral.0=#FFFFFF | 50=#F9FAFB | 100=#F3F4F6 | 200=#E5E7EB | 500=#6B7280 | 900=#111827 | 1000=#000000

### Spacing Tokens (only values from this scale)
space.1=4px, space.2=8px, space.3=12px, space.4=16px, space.5=20px,
space.6=24px, space.8=32px, space.10=40px, space.12=48px,
space.16=64px, space.20=80px, space.24=96px

### Typography Tokens
font.family: display/body="Inter", mono="JetBrains Mono" (Thai/Lao fallback: Noto Sans Thai/Lao)
font.size: xs=12, sm=14, base=16, lg=18, xl=20, 2xl=24, 3xl=30, 4xl=36 (px)
font.weight: regular=400, medium=500, semibold=600, bold=700
line.height: tight=1.25, normal=1.5, relaxed=1.75

### Radius Tokens
none=0, sm=4px, md=8px (default), lg=12px, xl=16px, 2xl=24px, full=9999px

### Shadow Tokens
shadow.sm | shadow.md | shadow.lg | shadow.xl only

### Motion Tokens
duration: instant=0, fast=100ms, normal=200ms (default), slow=300ms, slower=500ms
easing: default | in | out | spring

### Hard Constraints (never violate)
- CONSTRAINT-01: No colors outside the tokens
- CONSTRAINT-02: No hardcoded spacing/font-size/font-weight
- CONSTRAINT-03: No new components when one already exists in the DS — always check the components dir first
- CONSTRAINT-04: No shadows outside the elevation scale
- CONSTRAINT-05: No border-radius outside the radius scale
- CONSTRAINT-06: Every interactive element must have complete states (hover/active/disabled)
- CONSTRAINT-07: Touch targets ≥ 44x44px (mobile)
- CONSTRAINT-08: Color contrast WCAG AA (4.5:1 text, 3:1 large text)

## Project Context
- Framework: [React 18 / Next.js 14 / Flutter 3.x]
- Styling: [Tailwind CSS / CSS Modules / Styled Components]
- Token file (generated — DO NOT EDIT): [src/styles/tokens.ts]
- Token source: [tokens/*.json → Style Dictionary]
- Components directory: [src/components/]
- Breakpoints: xs<480, sm 480-767, md 768-1023, lg 1024-1279, xl 1280-1535, 2xl≥1536

## UI Implementation Rules
- Every visual value must come from the token file — no hex/px literals (CI will block them)
- New components: check the components dir + DS Component Index first — reuse before create
- Every new component gets a comment header:
  `// Figma: [node-id] - [component name]`
  `// DS: [DS Component name] / [variant]`
- Every component must have states: default, hover, active, disabled (+loading if async)
- Export component names matching the DS Component Index
- Before implementing a new screen: always read the handoff note first (ask the user if missing)
- After implementing: run a self token audit (scan for hardcoding) before reporting done

## Figma MCP
- If MCP reads a frame incompletely/unclearly: ask for a specific node ID, or request a screenshot of the frame to compare
- Never guess a design from a frame name — read it for real

